attributes.description: This dashboard provides insights into the network logs of macOS.

params.markdown:
### MacOS

#### Description

This dashboard provides an overview of macOS Unified Logs, helping security and operations teams monitor system and network activities across macOS devices. It highlights top message names, states, and tasks to identify recurring system activities. Tables further enrich the analysis by listing active network connections, supporting efficient investigation and performance monitoring.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/macos/overview)**
